  <thing id="sArt1001" name="Armor Enhancement, Lesser" description="The armor or shield you touch temporarily gains a special ability commonly found on magic armor or shields. You can choose any special ability whose market price is equivalent to a +1 bonus or up to 5,000 gp, such as light fortification or shadow. The armor or shield does not need to have an existing enhancement bonus, nor does it gain one when you imbue it with this infusion.\n\n{i}Material Component{/i}: An ointment made from rare spices and minerals, costing 10 gp." compset="Spell" summary="Armor or shield gains special ability with +1 bonus market price modifier.">
