  <thing id="sArt3005" name="Metamagic Item" description="You temporarily apply a metamagic feat you know to a single spell contained within a spell trigger item. For the duration of this infusion, anyone who casts that spell from the item gains the benefit of that metamagic feat. For example, you could imbue a {i}wand of fireballs{/i} with the Empower Spell feat or apply the Maximize Spell feat to the {i}cone of cold{/i} spell in a {i}staff of frost{/i}." compset="Spell" summary="Imbue spell trigger item with metamagic feat.">
