  <thing id="sArt3006" name="Power Surge" description="By touching a wand or staff that has at least 1 charge, you imbue it with 1 temporary charge per five caster levels. These charges work like temporary hit points: When a character uses the item, deduct the charges spent from the temporary charges first. When the {i}power surge{/i} expires, any remaining temporary charges are lost.\n\n{i}XP Cost{/i}: 5 XP &#215; the level of the highest-level spell stored in the item." compset="Spell" summary="Charged spell trigger item gains temporary charges.">
