  <thing id="sArt5003" name="Major Creation" description="This spell functions like {i}minor creation{/i}, except that you can also create an object of mineral nature: stone, crystal, metal, or the like. The duration of the created item varies with its relative hardness and rarity, as indicated on the following table.\n\n{b}Hardness and Rarity Examples &#151; Duration{/b}\nVegetable matter &#151; 2 hr./level\nStone, crystal, base metals &#151; 1 hr./level\nPrecious metals &#151; 20 min./level\nGems &#151; 10 min./level\nRare metal* &#151; 1 round/level\n* Includes adamantine, alchemical silver, and mithral. You can&#146;t use major creation to create a cold iron item. See the Dungeon Master&#146;s Guide for details." compset="Spell" summary="As minor creation, plus stone and metal.">
